shadowman.repository
Class SimpleObjectFileRepository

java.lang.Object
  shadowman.repository.SimpleObjectFileRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
Repository<String,Serializable>
public class SimpleObjectFileRepository
extends Object
implements Repository<String,Serializable>

A Repository implementation maintaining all elements under a single root directory. The root directory will be created automatically if it does not all ready exist.
